  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1181732/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/07/07/7cb8a95e850eea70aa015854147fa584.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1181732\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t本文声优：能猫</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">你</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">想拥有和声优一样的流利口语吗？戳这里&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/classzt/MKTTopic_p92121?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=be388e8c\" target=\"_blank\">体验外教1对1口语</a></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">At 12, I believed honesty was always rewarded.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">十二岁时，我以为诚实总会有回报。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">One afternoon, I hit a ball through a&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"https://dict.hjenglish.com/w/vacant\" target=\"_blank\">vacant</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;apartment&rsquo;s window.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">一天下午，我不小心将球踢进了一间空公寓的窗户中。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The sound of shattering glass was followed by kids running in all directions screaming, &ldquo;Run! No one will tell.&rdquo;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">一声窗户玻璃碎裂的声音后，小伙伴们四下逃窜，边跑边喊：&ldquo;快跑，没有人会知道的！&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">I went to the manager, expecting praise for being so honest. He laughed, saying, &ldquo;I&rsquo;ve never had a kid snitch on themselves. Kind of dumb.&rdquo;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">而我找到了大楼的经理，希望他会表扬我的诚实。他笑了，说：&ldquo;我还从来没见过像你这样主动告密的蠢孩子呢。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">I didn&rsquo;t understand until my mother said, &ldquo;How did you feel when you told the truth? Remember that instead of what he said.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Pride in yourself will always be your reward.&rdquo;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">我对此很是不解，这时，妈妈告诉我：&ldquo;忘记他所说的，只需记住你讲真话时的感受。诚实所带来的骄傲是永恒的回报。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t（翻译：进击的Meredith）</p>\n<p class=\"declaration-text\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1181732/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1181732\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768361/\">有声双语美文：你的生活也可以满满全是爱！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1203990/\">中国人每天使用最多的app，居然不是微信？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1203490/\">查尔斯王子遭英国民众抵制，继任王位基本无望</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1080054/\">Quora精选：在麻省理工上学是什么感觉？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1203500/\">阿里巴巴要用自动贩卖机卖车？马云你没事吧</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1203430/\">脸书打入中国决心不减，新app在中国试运行！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1203433/\">汤姆•克鲁斯拍摄《碟中谍6》意外受伤</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1203502/\">小贝大儿子将赴美国学摄影，将“消失”几年</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1182465/\">30个以-ible和-able结尾的单词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1203856